Temple is a music track that is unlocked in Temple of Marimbo dungeon, and in the cavern containing the M'amulet mould.

Versions[edit | edit source]

Version Release Music Track
1 June – October 2004
2 6 March 2007

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • According to data crowdsourced via RuneLite, approximately 99.6% of players unlock the track in the cavern, while 0.4% unlock it in the Temple of Marimbo. This is because it is pointless, and potentially dangerous, to visit the Temple before the player has the M'amulet mould.
